Installing gcc-9 and this version of cmake in this way is a little hard to maintain.
I am wondering if it makes sense to just go to focal.
@aajisaka upgraded to bionic in HADOOP-16054.
I wonder if we should just upgrade to focal as it is LTS.
@ayushtkn you were also involved in that upgrade; what are your thoughts on upgrading to focal?

@goiri , @aajisaka , @ayushtkn I tried to upgrade to Focal and it seems like a lot of unit tests are failing - #2613 (comment).
I ran all the tests on the current trunk and interestingly, there are already so many existing unit test failures - #2623 (comment)
I would like to request that we decouple this PR from upgrading to Focal and proceed with the review of this PR.
